    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  first diagnosis cardiovascular disease

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Severe liver and kidney disease or cancer

          -  Limb movement disorder

          -  Cognitive impairment

          -  History of malignant arrhythmia or severe heart failure patients have a high risk of
             sudden death

          -  Diabetes

          -  Cerebrovascular disease

          -  History of atherosclerotic disease hospital
      </textblock>
